          <span class="italic">The General Assembly</span>,</p>
      </formula>
      <container name="Having considered" eId="container_2">
        <p xml:space="preserve">	<span class="italic">Having considered</span> the report of the Secretary-General on a post-traumatic stress disorder framework for uniformed personnel<authorialNote marker="1" placement="bottom" eId="authorialNote_1"><p xml:space="preserve">	 	<a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/76/662">A/76/662</a>.</p></authorialNote> and the related report of the Advisory Committee on Administrative and Budgetary Questions,<authorialNote marker="2" placement="bottom" eId="authorialNote_2"><p xml:space="preserve">	 	<a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/76/782">A/76/782</a>.</p></authorialNote> </p>
